Package eapli.base.surveymanagement.grammar.answerverifier.generated

Interface AnswerVerifierListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnswerVerifierBaseListener
    public interface AnswerVerifierListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by AnswerVerifierParser.
